<p>In the evening, Faith couldn't fall asleep. Sure, she had no problem the previous night, but she missed Buffy's closeness. She knew Buffy didn't return her feelings, but that didn't stop Faith from wanting to be near her. And strangely enough, she didn't even felt the need to have sex with Buffy, she just wanted to be with her. She hesitated for a while and then went to Buffy's room. After all, Buffy had offered to stay with her. She hesitated for a few moments and then knocked on the door.</p>
